data.description: This ranch-style, brick charmer is sure to warm and invite. Built-in desk for a cozy work from home center is conveniently located between the three bedrooms and the kitchen on the main level. Beautiful hardwood floors flank the kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Nearly ten thousand square feet of a Colorado perfect backyard! Store your RV, jump on the in-ground trampoline, take a dip in the hit tub, and entertain in the outdoor living space. Bring the fun indoors to the basement wet bar and pool table. Let your guests stay in the basement flex room next to laundry and their own bath. This well-built ranch is waiting for your personal touch to make it your dream home.
